  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IProgressRecorder
    Callback for reporting progress.

    Interface for objects that can provide progress updates.

    Interface for objects that can provide a stream.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChecksummingInputStream
    An IValidatingInputStream that wraps another input stream and validates against a provided checksum.
    MergedInputStream
    InputStream that merges multiple other InputStreams.
    ParallelHttpGetInputStream
    An InputStream that reads a resource in parallel from multiple urls by fetching ranges of the file on multiple threads.
    ReadAheadInputStream
    An InputStream that reads ahead in the background and buffers data via the file system.
    ValidatingInputStream
    An InputStream that can validate itself.
